name: Endless Pinball Loop 01
description:
[05-10-18] 
I don't remember much about creating this one, but it seems that once again I was inspired by one of my enjoyments: Pinball, and perhaps also my early fascination for George Rhoads work.
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Rhoads
I remember as a child seeing a cool kinetic art installation he made, in a mall in Plattsburgh and couldn't look away from it. 
It was made with trapcode TAO in After Effects.

[26-06-21]
For a little bit of continuation with the last piece, next going on to more random stuff
minting this 1:1 | 1080x1080 | 180 FRAMES | 30FPS
